request.description:
**Purpose:** Get paginated list of companies with totalAssets and totalUsers.

**Who Uses it:** system admin

**When to call it:** on admin dashboard or admin companies tab.

**Params: (optional)**

//companyName:  
//isActive: true/false  
//sortBy:createdAt:desc/aesc  
//limit:10  
//page:1

