**Purpose:** Get consolidated dashboard data in a single API call.

**Who Uses it:**
- **system_admin**: Gets global stats (total companies, users, assets, QR codes) + recent companies list
- **customer_admin**: Gets company-specific stats + recent users

**Response (system_admin):**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "stats": {
    "totalCompanies": 15,
    "totalUsers": 150,
    "totalAssets": 500,
    "totalQRCodes": 1000
  },
  "recentCompanies": [
    {
      "_id": "...",
      "companyName": "Company Name",
      "contactEmail": "email@company.com",
      "createdAt": "2024-01-15T10:30:00Z",
      "totalUsers": 10
    }
  ]
}
```

**Response (customer_admin):**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "company": {
    "companyName": "My Company",
    "contactEmail": "admin@mycompany.com",
    "settings": {...},
    "isActive": true
  },
  "stats": {
    "totalUsers": 25,
    "totalAssets": 100,
    "totalQRCodes": 150
  },
  "recentUsers": [...]
}
```
